---
// Honeymoon fund section
---

<section class="content-section py-20">
	<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
		<div class="text-center mb-16">
			<div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-white/20 rounded-full mb-6 backdrop-blur-sm">
				<svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
					<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
				</svg>
			</div>
			<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-light text-white mb-4 drop-shadow-lg">
				Lua de Mel
			</h2>
			<div class="w-24 h-px bg-white/60 mx-auto"></div>
		</div>
		
		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
			<div class="text-center md:text-left">
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-medium text-white mb-6 drop-shadow-md">
					Ajudem-nos a criar memórias inesquecíveis
				</h3>
				<div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-white/90 leading-relaxed drop-shadow-md">
					<p>
						Querem fazer parte da nossa lua de mel? Estamos a planear uma 
						aventura incrível entre <strong>Singapura</strong> e <strong>Bali</strong>. 
						Cada pequeno contributo será transformado em momentos memoráveis 
						(e muitos cocktails à beira-mar! 🍹).
					</p>
					<p>
						Mas, acima de tudo, o melhor presente será sem dúvida a vossa 
						presença neste dia tão especial.
					</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
					<div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-6 border border-white/20">
						<h4 class="text-xl font-medium text-white mb-4 drop-shadow-md">
							💳 MBWAY
						</h4>
						<div class="space-y-3">
							<div>
								<p class="text-sm text-white/80 mb-1">Tânia:</p>
								<p class="font-mono text-lg text-white font-semibold drop-shadow-md">
									916 702 436
								</p>
							</div>
							<div>
								<p class="text-sm text-white/80 mb-1">Miguel:</p>
								<p class="font-mono text-lg text-white font-semibold drop-shadow-md">
									910 661 162
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					
					<div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-6 border border-white/20">
						<h4 class="text-xl font-medium text-white mb-4 drop-shadow-md">
							🏦 Transferência Bancária
						</h4>
						<p class="text-sm text-white/80 mb-2">IBAN:</p>
						<p class="font-mono text-lg text-white font-semibold drop-shadow-md">
							PT50 0269 0195 00204538094 22
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="relative">
				<div class="space-y-6">
					<div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-6 border border-white/20">
						<h4 class="text-xl font-medium text-white mb-4 drop-shadow-md flex items-center">
							🌴 Bali
						</h4>
						<div class="aspect-w-4 aspect-h-3 rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-4">
							<img src="images/bali.jpg" alt="Terraços de arroz em Bali" class="object-cover w-full h-full" />
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<div class="mt-16 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-8 text-center border border-white/20">
			<h4 class="text-xl font-medium text-white mb-4 drop-shadow-md">
				💕 O mais importante
			</h4>
			<p class="text-white/90 mb-6 drop-shadow-md">
				A vossa presença no nosso casamento é o presente mais precioso! 
				Qualquer contributo será usado para criar memórias inesquecíveis na nossa lua de mel.
			</p>
			<p class="text-white/80 text-sm drop-shadow-md">
				Obrigada por fazerem parte desta aventura connosco! ✈️🏝️
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
